  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Silica is a crossover of FPS and RTS, where you take part in epic photorealistic battles either as humans or aliens. Lead as the commander, or join the assault from the ground - the choice is yours! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/dd6faf3eb191c21dfe2b1e10a51eeaea.poster.avif?t=1765552519\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/dd6faf3eb191c21dfe2b1e10a51eeaea.webm?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/dd6faf3eb191c21dfe2b1e10a51eeaea.mp4?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take Part in Epic Combined Arms Warfare</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in epic battles where humans and aliens fight for ultimate domination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dominate Land and Sky</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of both land and air vehicles to assert power over the sandy dunes of planet Baltarus</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/4dccef1e8c1d001bbc5776525d74bee5.poster.avif?t=1765552519\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/4dccef1e8c1d001bbc5776525d74bee5.webm?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/4dccef1e8c1d001bbc5776525d74bee5.mp4?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lead as RTS Commander!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take charge as RTS commander over battles of epic scale. Use your tactical prowess to dominate the battlefield, coordinating complex operations from a top-down perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/4a9248247a93233a7c1e9356394b2458.poster.avif?t=1765552519\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/4a9248247a93233a7c1e9356394b2458.webm?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/4a9248247a93233a7c1e9356394b2458.mp4?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience Realistic Unit Scale</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Witness the impressive scale of units, from small infantry squads to colossal harvesters and massive buildings. Each unit type is meticulously designed to reflect its size, providing an immersive and realistic experience on the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/753f1ac03addacf637acd54722ddcd97.poster.avif?t=1765552519\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/753f1ac03addacf637acd54722ddcd97.webm?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/753f1ac03addacf637acd54722ddcd97.mp4?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SIEGE MODE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This exciting game mode is all about intense, close-quarters combat, whether you are playing solo or teaming up with friends. Protect your base against relentless hordes of enemies or attack your opponent as a Soldier or Commander! Load your weapons, suit up and prepare for battle to stay in control of the battlefield.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Silica is a crossover of FPS and RTS, where you take part in epic photorealistic battles either as humans or aliens. Lead as the commander, or join the assault from the ground - the choice is yours! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/dd6faf3eb191c21dfe2b1e10a51eeaea.poster.avif?t=1765552519\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/dd6faf3eb191c21dfe2b1e10a51eeaea.webm?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/dd6faf3eb191c21dfe2b1e10a51eeaea.mp4?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take Part in Epic Combined Arms Warfare</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in epic battles where humans and aliens fight for ultimate domination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dominate Land and Sky</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of both land and air vehicles to assert power over the sandy dunes of planet Baltarus</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/4dccef1e8c1d001bbc5776525d74bee5.poster.avif?t=1765552519\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/4dccef1e8c1d001bbc5776525d74bee5.webm?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/4dccef1e8c1d001bbc5776525d74bee5.mp4?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lead as RTS Commander!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take charge as RTS commander over battles of epic scale. Use your tactical prowess to dominate the battlefield, coordinating complex operations from a top-down perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/4a9248247a93233a7c1e9356394b2458.poster.avif?t=1765552519\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/4a9248247a93233a7c1e9356394b2458.webm?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/4a9248247a93233a7c1e9356394b2458.mp4?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience Realistic Unit Scale</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Witness the impressive scale of units, from small infantry squads to colossal harvesters and massive buildings. Each unit type is meticulously designed to reflect its size, providing an immersive and realistic experience on the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/753f1ac03addacf637acd54722ddcd97.poster.avif?t=1765552519\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/753f1ac03addacf637acd54722ddcd97.webm?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494420/extras/753f1ac03addacf637acd54722ddcd97.mp4?t=1765552519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SIEGE MODE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This exciting game mode is all about intense, close-quarters combat, whether you are playing solo or teaming up with friends. Protect your base against relentless hordes of enemies or attack your opponent as a Soldier or Commander! Load your weapons, suit up and prepare for battle to stay in control of the battlefield.</p>",
